Phase 7 - Quality loop
[ ] Add lesson quality checklist:
    [ ] Does it combine all selected materials?
    [ ] Is the structure logical?
    [ ] Are explanations understandable for digital marketing agency employees?
    [ ] Are key concepts explained clearly?
    [ ] Are examples used where they help understanding?
    [ ] Are important caveats preserved?
[ ] Add regeneration/improvement options:
    [ ] Make simpler.
    [ ] Make deeper.
    [ ] Add more examples.
    [ ] Make more structured.
    [ ] Shorten.
[ ] Consider user feedback:
    [ ] Rate generated lesson.
    [ ] Add feedback before regeneration.

Phase 8 - Testing
[ ] Unit test material aggregation and validation.
[ ] Unit test prompt builder with sample materials and instructions.
[ ] Integration test lesson generation happy path.
[ ] Test failure cases:
    [x] No materials handled in frontend and backend validation.
    [ ] Oversized materials.
    [x] AI/API failure saves failed lesson and returns error.
    [ ] Invalid/empty AI output.
[x] Manual prompt inspection through Build prompt button.
[ ] Manual QA with 2-3 real onboarding material sets.
    [x] First QA found prompt was too course-like and had too much filler.
    [x] Prompt v2 adjusted to remove Short Description, Learning Objectives, Lesson Outline, and unsupported filler.
    [ ] Re-test prompt v2 on Google Ads launch / naming convention material.

